    # "Sarah advanced on the man, repeating the attack patern that she had practiced more than she could remember."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_fca13788:
    # "The Tribesman's art was more graceful, spinning and twisting in ways that were only possible for someone carrying little armor."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_919ac2e5:
    # "He spun, his blade catching her own, blocking his strike."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_31779c49:
    # "Sarah, for her part, focussed on her own footwork."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_681a58cc:
    # "The Tribesman was deadly, but the ground, now turned to mud, was equally dangerous."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0a98ae0c:
    # "One slip and she'd be done for."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_aca6768d:
    # "Sarah gripped the handle of her blade with both hands."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_39c62175:
    # "Swinging the sword overhead with all the force she could muster, she struck at the Tribesman."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d934fa02:
    # "Again, he spun, twisting his body, deflecting her attacks with his curved blade."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b426fa3e:
    # "Sarah continued her advance, swinging her blade with the same practiced pace."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_fe39770d:
    # "Their blades clattered, ringing out as they moved across the chaotic melee."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f240e1b1:
    # "The Tribesman lashed out at her, but his blade bounced off her armor."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a16efec8:
    # "Suddenly, Sarah stepped forward, closing the distance between them."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_240b77a0:
    # "Catching his arm before he could pull it back, Sarah gripped the Tribesman, pulling him close."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1283413d:
    # "Wrestling, the two of them stumbled about."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_588eeb23:
    # "Too close, neither could properly swing their blade at the other."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a49f30b9:
    # "But Sarah understood this sooner."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e4ea0aaa:
    # "Striking the Tribesman in the face with her free hand, she heard his nose break."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d86ea26d:
    # "As she kept him entangled, she brought her hand down on his face, again and again."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b8d3b648:
    # "His resistance slowly yielded, until he was little more than a ragdoll in her grip."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_bcff0f1c:
    # "Releasing her grip on him, his body fell to the ground."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a61a015f:
    # "With all the force left in her body, Sarah raised her leg and brought it down."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_71af8058:
    # "The shattering sound of plated steel meeting brittle bone was one she hoped she could soon forget."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0fddc0d2:
    # "Sarah did not look down, she knew enough that he was dead."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_9328b831:
    # "She turned her head."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3f1cbaa9:
    # "Just in time, she saw Kate drive her blade through the remaining Tribesman's chest."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_bb91f51d:
    # "The man fell backwards onto the ground, a gurgling noise, then death."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7101571c:
    # "Sarah saw Kate, her face covered in blood."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0bdcbd9d:
    # s "Kate! Are you-"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_264f4182:
    # k "I'm fine!"
    k ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f06ae8e6:
    # "Kate was nearly screaming."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8e723ea0:
    # k "It's not my blood...mostly."
    k ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_625ec725_1:
    # s "But-"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f14623d7:
    # k "Just fall back to the backline!"
    k ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0fb793b8:
    # k "Organize the attack from the rear!"
    k ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_40aa162e_2:
    # "Sarah nodded."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5a46313b:
    # "She knew Kate was right."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_bcc83677:
    # "Saying nothing else, Sarah turned and began to run."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_66c77ffa:
    # "Sarah felt every muscle in her body scream, but she would not yield."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8e668248:
    # "She rushed through the lines of soldiers, retreating from the melee."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8a2e537c:
    # "Frantically, she pushed men aside, screaming for them to let her pass."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d539e8b5:
    # s "Let me through!"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c10a3776:
    # "Slowly, with each passing step, the chaos of the melee was further and further behind."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_138ef7a6:
    # "Finally, she broke through the last of them, reaching the rear of her army."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d2447d05:
    # "Sarah stumbled to the ground, but swiftly pushed herself back onto her feet."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a9d3ca8c:
    # "There was no time to stop."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f94b3c87:
    # s "Horse!"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6336123d:
    # "She looked about."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6f03c855:
    # s "Get me a fucking horse, now!"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6fc12391:
    # "A panicked scout ran over."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_edae8d83:
    # "Scout" "Commander! Are you-"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ea010bb1:
    # s "Your horse, now!"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_41974fb9:
    # "Scout" "I...of course!"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_606957ab:
    # "The young man dismounted, giving his horse to her."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_66bc1695:
    # "Sarah mounted as swiftly as she could."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_eb9a3517:
    # "As soon as she was atop the horse, she could look out across her army again."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_293eef23:
    # "From the higher vantage point, she surveyed the battle."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0bc886dc:
    # "Just as she had thought, the Tribesman army had made a mad dash for her position."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4eea6d84:
    # "But with her now safely out of reach, their charge had come to a halt."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_03d00305:
    # s "You!"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_304c556b:
    # "Sarah pointed at one of the scouts."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8a8b6ed4:
    # s "Ride up along the right flank, tell them to advance!"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8935995d:
    # s "Tell them to close up the gap, prevent the Tribesman from falling back!"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_85c5e268:
    # "The man nodded and raced off in a franctic pace."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_03d00305_1:
    # s "You!"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_05d7f7b5:
    # "She pointed at another."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4d2788bc:
    # s "Report the same to the left flank, move!"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_014a1dc1:
    # "Another messenger raced off with similar haste."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1fef2acc:
    # "Sarah looked out across her army and saw the Tribesman's charge falter."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2289336e:
    # "There were now several lines between herself and the enemy, and their progess had grinded to a halt."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_89c17f8f:
    # "Still, even from this distance, Sarah could see they were fighting like demons."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b1419ce9:
    # "A lesser army might have surrendered."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_157d0ba8:
    # "But these men were eager for a good death."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3ede36d1:
    # "And Sarah was eager to give it to them."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5ea06850:
    # "She saw how her commands were relayed and her army sprung to life."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_11ad598b:
    # "The flanks on each far end of her army began to move forward."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b604f7b0:
    # "Wrapping around the center, they closed off the only escape that had been available to the Tribesmen."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_16ffcfa3:
    # "Sarah watched as less then a few dozen Tribesmen realized what was happening and managed to escape the encirclement."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1d2a375e:
    # "The others, too lost in the frenzy of battle, did not retreat."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f025a6ac:
    # "The flanking units, mostly spearmen, had not yet seen battle and were eager for it."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ca87f087:
    # "Attacking the Tribesmen from behind, they found easy targets that were exhausted and caught by surprise."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_dce36a52:
    # "With heavy shields and long spears, even the common Rosannan footsoldier found it easy to kill these sons of war."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_796d8228:
    # "Pressed on all sides, surrounded, the Tribesmen continued to fight."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_9d5bf037:
    # "But their position had deteriorated so quickly that even they struggled to adapt."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_673e7987:
    # "While each of them was reduced to fighting as a single warrior, her army moved as one."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_442f2df2:
    # "The advancing Rosannan army pushed the Tribesmen together from all sides."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c77cfca7:
    # "Their great advantage, their horses, turned meaningless in the frenzy of such a close melee."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_25c11be3:
    # "Sarah smiled as she saw the core of the Tribesmen formation shrink."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d54b7f46:
    # "One by one, layer by layer, her army took the Tribesmen forces apart."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5a92e49c:
    # "They had gambled a lot on the hope that they might kill her and break apart her army."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ed7857d4:
    # "But they had fallen short."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a1fc0721:
    # "And in war, there was no partial victory."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_03d00305_2:
    # s "You!"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_dd409134:
    # "Sarah called another messenger over."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1fd84fc6:
    # s "Report along the line, finish up the last of the Tribesmen, then reposition to move on the capital."
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b18d4c9c:
    # s "Also, instruct the engineers to keep firing, I want to see the city wall crumble."
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_9d0617a8:
    # "Scout" "Yes, Commander!"
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_adc7dec0:
    # "The young man rushed off along the length of the line, spreading her instructions as fast as he could manage."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b61e3362:
    # "In little time at all, the last of the Tribesmen were put to death."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6abb738f:
    # "Once the victory had become clear, a mad zeal seemed to spread through the formation."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6e040000:
    # "No longer were they hesitant for war. They were hungry for it."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3021a519:
    # "Sarah heard them sing out their battle songs in eager anticipation for marching on the city."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7d06fb87:
    # "They had feared the Tribesmen, as well they should have, but now they learned they were as mortal as any other man."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_08e4aa7c:
    # "They could be broken."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1e33f336:
    # "Sarah watched her army fall back into formation."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f04828e1:
    # "Overhead, she saw the boulders of the trebuchets, flying across the sky, striking the outer walls of the city."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_72265c02:
    # "Larges plumes of dust rose up."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f65f2eef:
    # "Stones, scattering, walls breaking, the violent roar of the siege."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_df5d1749:
    # "Sarah looked at one of her officers."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1a70338c:
    # s "What is the situation with the Tribesmen?"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7326f886:
    # "Officer" "This attack was a large portion of their forces, but it wasn't all of them."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_40aa162e_3:
    # "Sarah nodded."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6655e277:
    # s "How many remain?"
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_00f705aa:
    # "Officer" "Hard to say, they're hiding behind their walls."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_a50da987:
    # "Officer" "Best estimate, maybe less than five-thousand."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_40aa162e_4:
    # "Sarah nodded."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_96c1abbf:
    # "A sizeable force, but far fewer than she had in her own army."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_81beec38:
    # "Still, when she moved into the city, it would be a brutal slog."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_09ae0d69:
    # "Block-by-block, she would have to fight her way through the city. Attacks could come from any direction."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c0385b89:
    # "And the march to Castle Reinmeer was long."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5efb54f3:
    # "Then there was the Castle itself, no easy target itself."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1a25fe1e:
    # "Still, it had to be done."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5c1caf28:
    # "Sarah watched the walls of the city until finally a large boulder struck true."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f08a510e:
    # "The integrity of the entire length of the wall gave out all at once."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1e0b69e7:
    # "Along the rest of the wall, Sarah saw other gaps emerge. Even the city gate seemed close to collapsing."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_793e6299:
    # "Sarah grabbed the horn that was tied to her waist."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0b381f29:
    # "She drew in as much air as she could, filling her lungs, and brought the horn to her lips."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4db03920:
    # "Exhaling with great force, she let out a titanous blast from the horn."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d12bbeeb:
    # "The deep, pounding sound seemed to reverberate into her bones."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1a29661e:
    # "All at once, her army began to march, advancing on the city."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_faab1e03:
    # "Sarah lowered the horn and watched in awe at the sheer size of her army."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_2780dd63:
    # "Remaining near the rear, she advanced along with her army, staying wary of any other surprise attacks."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_91c4e4e0:
    # "Her army could win the battle, but if she died the blow to morale could undo much of their advantage."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_29d91055:
    # "She didn't enjoy letting others risk their lives on her account, but she also knew she wasn't just one person anymore."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_db436519:
    # "Looking upon her home, she knew she was becoming so much more."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_cb554cdf:
    # "The army crossed the field."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7fee1a11:
    # "A few arrows fell on them as they advanced, but the large volley she had expected did not come."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8c861d53:
    # "The Tribesmen were experienced in war, but sieges were something they had far less experience with."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ef43951d:
    # "Least of all, defending from a siege."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_4f2a61c4:
    # "It was then perhaps no surprise they had failed to prepare as well as they could have."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1065439c:
    # "As they neared the walls of the city, the gaps were large enough for her soldiers to advance safely."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_073e2163:
    # "Her army moved into the city, passing through the damaged sections of the wall."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1e2ecd5d:
    # "They were hardly more than a few steps in when the Tribesmen began their attack."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_be72ff64:
    # "Using the narrow streets of the capital to their advantage, they hoped to compensate for their smaller numbers."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_13ad52bb:
    # "Arrows, shot from windows and rooftops."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_946e2e45:
    # "Small groups, carrying out cavalry charges, hitting and running, only to dissapear in some side-street."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_cb091d03:
    # "They were trying to bleed her army out."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_bcf7c9e1:
    # "But on her orders, her army kept advancing."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6e0a7d8c:
    # "Sarah knew that with her numbers, her advantage was too significant."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_54e47e5b:
    # "And so, despite the ongoing attacks from the Tribesmen, her army advanced deeper and deeper into the capital."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f2dd45f9:
    # "As they all slowly passed through the broken walls, the streets of the city began to swell with soldiers."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d162f679:
    # "Where at first the Tribesmen had been able to attack and dissapear into small streets, now Sarah's soldiers covered every angle."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6b47dae8:
    # "More and more of them flooded every part of the city."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_31c05cb5:
    # "And with each street and square lost, the Tribesmen were pushed back into a smaller part of the city."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ea437703:
    # "Already, Sarah could hear the cries of joy from the citizens, locked in their houses."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1be3cc3d:
    # "As the Tribesmen lost ground, they found themselves increasingly concentrated into smaller and smaller spaces."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ae4935e0:
    # "Their hit-and-run tactics were increasingly becoming futile."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_07a36bdf:
    # "When they did attack now, they did so in larger numbers. More regular fighting."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_fd6fa54b:
    # "But that kind of fighting took its toll."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_342331f9:
    # "It took its toll on both sides, but the Tribesmen did not have the numbers to spare for such a grinding conflict."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f59e5b31:
    # "Sarah watched as their numbers dwindled."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b029943a:
    # "How with each passing moment, the Tribesmen fell back further, surrendering more ground."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d1a7811a:
    # "By now, most of the city had been liberated."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d97e5bd8:
    # "And the only place to fall back to for the Tribesmen, was the Castle."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_7b54619f:
    # "Sarah pressed her forces on, giving pursuit to the Tribesmen forces."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_17761744:
    # "Finally, they relented and retreated all the way into the castle proper."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b277039e:
    # "Letting the gate fall shut behind them, they withdrew to their last and final position."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5a346154:
    # "Sarah watched as their haggard forces tried to set up their last defense."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_88232176:
    # "Her own forces had been wounded, but for the most part, her army was still plenty able to keep on the fight."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_add0c73c:
    # "It was the Tribesmen that had ran out of steam."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c9d0049e:
    # "The central road of the city that led up to the Castle was the most direct route of attack."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_32332c99:
    # "It would also be the quickest way to end this."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d8464b7a:
    # s "Send up the vanguard, have them take the castle gates. Once they're open, move up the rest of our forces."
    s ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d8db73e3:
    # "As ordered, Sarah watched her vanguard unit advance on the castle."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f7034c59:
    # "The vanguard consisted of the best soldiers from her mercenary company and Rosannan Knights that had survived The Fall."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_ed68ff4c:
    # "Her most experienced soldiers, they would make for more than a decent match to the Tribesmen."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_276c07ca:
    # "As they moved on the castle gates, the Tribesmen tried to stop their advance by firing arrows."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_991119c1:
    # "But the heavy plated armor and large shields of the vanguard unit meant that not a single arrow found purchase."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6fd4e6bc:
    # "Reaching the castle gates, they brought out their siege axes and got to work."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_6a527266:
    # "With each swing, they chipped away at the large, solid wood door that blocked the entrance into the castle."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_1c78bf3f:
    # "The gates of Castle Reinmeer were solid, but even they could not endure forever."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_477294b6:
    # "Meanwhile, so close to the gate, the Tribesmen could no longer properly fire their arrows, leaving the vanguard to hack away."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_9175bea8:
    # "Eventually, Sarah saw the door splinter."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_cb129fcd:
    # "A hole, large enough for maybe two men to move through."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_5770b0d3:
    # "Without wasting a moment, they did."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b7c0cd90:
    # "On the other side, they found the Tribesmen waiting for them, attacking as they tried to move through."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c517b19b:
    # "At first, the vanguard struggled, but with each man that moved through, they were able to push the Tribesmen back further."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3ca01e9c:
    # "Before long, they had secured their position on the other end of the door and pushed the Tribesmen back into the Castle square."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_8c5dbcde:
    # "Rather than advance further, the vanguard seized the Castle gate."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_9888c444:
    # "Pulling on the winch, they activated the machinery that had held the gates closed."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_0c207009:
    # "They swung open with a deep and heavy thud."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_3c5ca571:
    # "Sarah heard her own army scream out in celebration as they saw that the final obstacle to their victory had been thrown open."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f8a02e42:
    # "Before she could even issue the command, she saw her soldiers running up the road towards the castle."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_148d6aab:
    # "Each was eager not to be denied their share of the glory of this day."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_40323151:
    # "The vanguard fell back, allowing the core of the army to move into the castle."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_38f2a2d3:
    # "The Tribesmen fought bravely, but their numbers had dwindled so far that they could no longer mount a proper defense."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d3743d8e:
    # "Sarah's forces moved through the castle like a torrential surge, pushing through the Tribesmen forces."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_e53b4221:
    # "It was a battle for only a moment. Then it was a slaughter."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_f56873a6:
    # "Sarah entered the castle when most of the fighting had been settled."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_d12237ca:
    # "All about, she saw the bodies of the Tribesmen sprawled. Hacked up. Blood smeared."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_c7895ee3:
    # "Here and there, some of her own soldiers were being treated for injuries of their own."
    ""

translate ru WarriorQueen7Capital_b47e7ea1:
    # "A loud cheer rose up from the soldiers as they watched Sarah enter the castle grounds."
